data.description: Wellington floor plan by Bear Homes offers 4 bedrooms with additional 5th bedroom/office! Laundry room is conveniently located on the 2nd floor near the bedrooms. Bright  and airy kitchen with island for entertaining. Granite counter tops. Slate kitchen appliances are included to make this a move-in ready home for you! One year home warranty. 15 year dry basement warranty, 3rd party tested by Focus on Energy.  Newly remodeled Full basement is bright with lots of large windows on 3 sides with a full bath and kitchenette for recreation and entertaining.  Walkout basement with sliding door to large patio in back, must see.
